7 An Act relating to sexual assault nurse examiners;
amending Section 2, Chapter 343, O.S.L. 2023 (19 O.S.
8 Supp. 2025, Section 215.41), which relates to sexual
assault nurse examiners; and deleting sunset date.
9
10
11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 2, Chapter 343, O.S.L.
13 2023 (19 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 215.41), is amended to read as
14 follows:
15 Section 215.41. Subject to availability of funding, there is
16 established until October 1, 2025, within the District Attorneys
17 Council under the direction of the Executive Coordinator of the
18 District Attorneys Council, the position of Sexual Assault Nurse
19 Examiner (SANE) Statewide Coordinator. The Statewide Coordinator
20 shall oversee forensic medical examination training throughout the
21 state, recruit and develop SANE professionals, create and expand
22 local Sexual Assault Nurse Examiner programs and Sexual Assault
23 Response Team programs throughout this state, and coordinate
24 payments from the Sexual Assault Examination Fund.
